We recommended that the Management:

 Ensure that the 20% Development Fund is used only for its intended purpose;

 Always see to it that the Registry of Appropriations, Allotments and Obligations (RAAO) tallies/match with the Obligation Requests;

 Submit all the complete supporting documents needed as discussed above; and

 Ensure that the amount of actual ABC and ABC posted in the PhilGeps are the same/correct.

